  "detailed_description": "<strong>Factory Islands</strong> is a <strong>minimalist</strong> and <strong>relaxing</strong> experience where you must <strong>ensure</strong> the blocks in a way that they form a <strong>complete factory</strong> capable of transporting and refining ores before they reach their destination. Use conveyors, splitters, filters and tunnels to <strong>transport</strong> the ores correctly, but don't forget to use the furnaces and presses when it is necessary to <strong>refine and press</strong> the ores so that they arrive in the right form at your destination.<br><br><strong>Smelt ores with the Furnace and Press</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798100/extras/cd20548289ae2b7b2b3f5a06a6764af9.poster.avif?t=1729198548\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798100/extras/cd20548289ae2b7b2b3f5a06a6764af9.webm?t=1729198548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798100/extras/cd20548289ae2b7b2b3f5a06a6764af9.mp4?t=1729198548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>If you have an Energy Generator nearby, the Furnace and Press will transform all the ores that pass through them!<br><br><strong>Use Tunnels or Filters to transport the ores</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798100/extras/620cb2db8855961cd28a1f103df0d2cb.poster.avif?t=1729198548\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798100/extras/620cb2db8855961cd28a1f103df0d2cb.webm?t=1729198548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2798100/extras/620cb2db8855961cd28a1f103df0d2cb.mp4?t=1729198548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>6 resources</strong> to use in your factory;<br></li><li><strong>50 unique islands</strong>;<br></li><li><strong>4 environment variations</strong>;<br></li><li>Background music <strong>calm and relaxing</strong>;<br></li><li>Unique puzzles.<br></li><li>A <strong>minimalist and relaxing</strong> experience.</li></ul>",
